<w>kre<lb corresp="#b8"/><supplied>ntaunasa</supplied></w><caesura ana="frg:cs-s"/><gap reason="lost"/><w><supplied>skā</supplied>yoyträ</w><w>ṣañ</w><w>añ<supplied>mantse</supplied></w><w>kleśanma</w></p>
